# SCADAmon Sprite Generation Prompts
## For NanoBanana AI Image Generation

**Universal Style Prefix (add to ALL prompts):**
```
Game Boy Color pixel art, 64x64 sprite, limited 4-color palette per sprite, chunky pixels, clean edges, no anti-aliasing, retro 1998 Pokemon aesthetic,
```

---

